Created an attachment (id=70040)
proposed patch

We put in a check a while ago for when translators were unloading our resource without reason.  Well, when the file is deleted, there's a reason.  We now check to see if the file exists before reloading the resource.

submitted for approval ...
This is a low risk fix to allow XML resources to be correctly deleted without exceptions.  Given the very low risk level, I approve this patch.  It has been tested and reviewed.
